# FAB Menu & Action Sheet Standards

All floating action button menus (UniversalAddMenu, QuickAddSeed, QuickAddSupply) and bottom-sheet modals must follow these rules.

## Panel Background — always white

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT
className="... bg-white border border-neutral-200/80 ..."

// ❌ WRONG — cream is off-brand and visually inconsistent
className="... bg-cream ..."
className="... bg-neutral-50 ..."
```

## Backdrop Overlay — consistent across all FAB menus

Every FAB menu must render the same backdrop overlay directly before the panel div:

```tsx
<div className="fixed inset-0 z-[100] bg-black/20" aria-hidden onClick={onClose} />
<div className="fixed ... bg-white ...">
  {/* panel content */}
</div>
```

- Opacity is `bg-black/20` — not 0, not 50. Consistent across all menus.
- If one menu has it, all menus must have it. Never add/remove it from only one component.

## Positioning

| Component | Position |
|-----------|----------|
| UniversalAddMenu | `top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2` (centered) |
| QuickAddSeed | `bottom-20` (above bottom nav) |
| QuickAddSupply | `bottom-20` (above bottom nav) |

Do not change positioning between components without updating all three.

## Border Radius

All FAB menu panels use `rounded-3xl`. Action option rows inside use `rounded-3xl` for UniversalAddMenu and `rounded-xl` for QuickAddSeed/QuickAddSupply. Do not mix.
